# Canonical author / committer identities for the MemForge project.
#
# Format: <canonical name> <canonical-email> [<other-name>] [<other-email>]
# Lines without a mapping target declare the canonical form for that
# (name, email) pair without rewriting it. See `git help mailmap`.
#
# GitHub's web UI honors this file for commit-attribution rendering;
# `git log --use-mailmap` and `git shortlog` honor it on the CLI.
#
# To normalize a future contributor's commits whose name or email
# drifted across machines, add a line of the form:
#   Canonical Name <canonical@example.com> Other Name <other@example.com>

Mike Hiltz <mike@ildan.ai>
